{"tid":1882562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國據報擬禁通用出口客機引擎至中國　憂遭複製技術","createTime":"2020-02-16T10:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T10:55:51.000Z","uid":75656,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7257b17789e33d332f35db51095e3ae96de0202c","tid":1882562,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCbjieH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCbjieH.png&h=5cedfb45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報道，為防止中國透過逆向工程，以獲得製造引擎技術，美國政府擬將禁止通用電氣（GE）與法國賽峰集團（Safran）合資的CFM國際（CFM International）向中國出口飛機引擎，有機會影響中國第一款自行研發的C919大型商用客機投入服務。<br />\n<br />\n通用電氣自2014年起，獲得向中國製的C919客機提供引擎的許可證，最新一次獲批准出口是去年3月。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》引述消息人士報道，華府正在考慮不再發牌，通用電氣要停止出口這款引擎到中國，因美方認為，中國企業可能對已獲得的引擎進行「逆向工程」，從中取得引擎製造技術。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，美國政府多個部門將於周四舉行會議，討論限制美國向中國輸出技術的問題。而特朗普政府內閣亦會於本月28日召開會議討論相關議題，白宮與美國商務部，及通用電氣均拒評有關消息。報道指出，華府多年來一直支持美國公司與中國的民航企業做生意，包括容許出售引擎、飛行控制系統及其他飛機組件。<br />\n<br />\n中國第一款自行研發的C919大型商用客機，最多載客190人，料在2021年交付航空公司投入服務，有關客機仍要用外國生產的引擎，所使用 LEAP-1C引擎，由美國通用電氣和法國賽峰集團的合資公司CFM國際生產。通用電氣自2014年獲得許可，向中國出口LEAP-1C引擎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%93%AC%E7%A6%81%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%AE%A2%E6%A9%9F%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%86%82%E9%81%AD%E8%A4%87%E8%A3%BD%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%2593%25AC%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%2593%258E%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%2586%2582%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25A4%2587%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593%2F&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=f8a03d31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%2593%25AC%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%2593%258E%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%2586%2582%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25A4%2587%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593%2F&h=8c9f2b49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%93%AC%E7%A6%81%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%AE%A2%E6%A9%9F%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%86%82%E9%81%AD%E8%A4%87%E8%A3%BD%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93/</a>"},{"pid":"d0b52437ccac20fbf22a14a90b84e5c5d32f7e47","tid":1882562,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:37:31.000Z","msg":"立場畫畫嗰條友今次high邊隻毒品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e887d568a020b6594ef39f07773209b4ee1e98d6","tid":1882562,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:39:16.000Z","msg":"唔直接出口改做叫支那d 航空買架飛機再拆件出黎再自煮燃發？"},{"pid":"0f5da9996f465241a49268d32d890b8abea75398","tid":1882562,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"班美奸又出嚟大聲屌了"},{"pid":"9f52c0f195e5ed50057ff59a8440864e0e31d53e","tid":1882562,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:54:02.000Z","msg":"COMAC C919 jet advances on espionage suspicions<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.airway1.com/comac-c919-jet-advances-on-espionage-suspicions/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airway1.com%2Fcomac-c919-jet-advances-on-espionage-suspicions%2F&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=64d81227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http